      • convertValues2KB

        protected void convertValues2KB(HashMap conversionValues)
        Method that will overwrite the URL's stored in the database with the URL specified for Kaartenbalie. This new URL indicate the link to the kaartenbalie, while the old link is used to indicate the URL to the real location of the service. Because the client which is connected to kaartenbalie has to send his requests back to kaartenbalie and not directly to the official resource, the URL has to be replaced.
        Parameters:
        newUrl - String representing the URL the old URL has to be replaced with.

      • getIdentityMap

        public Map getIdentityMap(boolean includeServiceProviderAbbr)
        Get a map of tuples containing the identity of this layer, for purposes of comparing the identity maps of different layers. The includeServiceProviderAbbr can be used to create identity maps which do or do not include the service provider abbreviation. The properties which are always added to the map are getName(), getTitle() and getCascaded()
        Parameters:
        includeServiceProviderAbbr - if getServiceProvider().getAbbr() should be included in the map.
        Returns:
        A Map containing tuples of identifier properties
